subject: resource/Tokheim
object: Tokheim Group S.A.S. is a French-based manufacturer of fuel dispensers. It claims to be one of the world's leading manufacturers and servicers of fuel dispensing equipment. The group has operations in many countries and offers customers a complete range of fuel dispensers and pumps, retail automation systems, payment terminals, media devices, replacement parts and upgrade kits, and support services including service station construction and maintenance.
